OL,6,FFollowing consultation with the Crown
OL,7,FProsecution Service, Edmundson,
OL,8,Fformerly of Oswaldtwistle but now of
OL,9,Fno fixed address, was charged with
OL,10,Fengaging in sexual communication with
OL,11,Fa child; causing or inciting a child
OL,12,Fto engage in sexual activity;
OL,13,Fencouraging or assisting serious self-
OL,14,Fharm; and possessing indecent images
OL,15,Fof children.
OL,17,FHe pleaded guilty to all the offences
OL,18,Fwhen he appeared at Preston Crown
OL,19,FCourt earlier this year. He was back
OL,20,Fin the dock and was sentenced to five
OL,21,Fyears and three months in custody.
